00:02:15.760 --> 00:02:19.600
Tarantino used blacksploitation in making Jackie Brown

00:02:19.860 --> 00:02:26.920
Thereafter, he mixed martial art, Western spaghetti and Italian horror genres in Kill Bill 1 &amp; 2.

00:02:27.120 --> 00:02:30.220
